</taxonomicName>
O. P.-Cambridge (
<taxonomicName id="4C034D45FFFEFF97FE39FCE7FDD9540C" box="[392,532,846,873]" class="Arachnida" family="Segestriidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="11" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Segestriidae</taxonomicName>
), adult or subadult female. The wasp pulled the immobilized tube-dwelling spider backwards, dorsal side upward, across the ground for 
<quantity id="4CFB9B23FFFEFF97FCA8FCD8FC9254E9" box="[793,863,881,908]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="11" pageNumber="10" unit="cm" value="60.0">60 cm</quantity>
